metadata.name: I'm Not An Artist
metadata.description:
It's how I feel most of the time.  
___  
This was the first piece I created after deciding to start the "I'm not an artist" collection of 1/1s - but I never minted it because A) I wasn't sure it was good enough and B) I wanted to do something cool with the minting mechanics but didn't think I had enough presence to get any attention for it.

I often let contradicting feelings stop me from doing things... My ambition to always do something unique and my fear of not being able to deliver.  
___
